title: Betelgeuse and the Crab Nebula: Stellar Death and Rebirth
description: In 2019, Betelgeuse dimmed in brightness, sparking speculation that it may soon explode as a supernova. While it likely won’t explode quite yet, we can preview its fate by observing the nearby Crab Nebula.
